        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI've pulled down this code, built the plugin, loaded it onto a (Python 2.7-based) Cloudify Manager, and deployed a simple blueprint.   The deployment was successful--the earlier problem resulting from the missing import of \"cloudify_importer\" was resolved.\n\nSuggested merging 99340 (bumping versions for all of the plugins), then patching this change to bump the version to 1.7.1, then merging this change.",
